## Frontmatter contract
All non-daily notes must include:
  created: YYYY-MM-DD
  updated: YYYY-MM-DD
  type: fleeting | daily | lit | evergreen | project | area | moc | person
  tags: [kebab-case-tag]
  status: seedling | budding | evergreen

## Operating rules
- Read index.md before answering any non-trivial query
- Read _index.md in any folder before touching files in it
- Wikilinks: [[Note title]] — check target exists before linking
- Tags: kebab-case; do not invent new top-level tags
- Never modify raw/ or 80-Archive/
- Update _index.md and index.md when creating or deleting files
- At end of every session, write summary to 90-Meta/AI-Sessions/YYYY-MM-DD-topic.md

## Ingest workflow
When asked to "ingest <file>":
1. Read the source in raw/
2. Discuss key takeaways
3. Write a summary page in 40-Resources/learning/
4. Update relevant entity/concept pages in 50-Slipbox/ and 60-MOCs/
5. Update index.md with new pages
6. Append to log.md: ## [YYYY-MM-DD] ingest | <title>
